{"tid":673651,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Netflix和Obama夫婦簽約合作拍攝電影劇","createTime":"2018-05-22T04:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T07:03:19.000Z","uid":66943,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"654595c714560f4d9603daa8ea82f67a77274b31","tid":673651,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:42:37.000Z","msg":"Netflix宣布簽下了美國前總統Obama及其夫人。雙方就多個協議達成共識，將共同製作一系列內容，包括紀錄片、電影和劇集等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/05/20180522_gd_340_3/gamersky_01origin_01_20185221131997.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F05%2F20180522_gd_340_3%2Fgamersky_01origin_01_20185221131997.jpg&h=2ffd001d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nObama表示：&ldquo;擔任總統期間的樂趣之一，就是能遇見來自各行各業的人們，並幫助他們將經驗分享給更廣大的群體。這就是為什麼Michelle和我很高興能與Netflix合作。我們希望培養有才華、能鼓舞人、有創造性的聲音，能夠促進人們之間彼此有更多理解，幫助他們把他們的故事分享給世界。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/05/20180522_gd_340_3/gamersky_02origin_03_20185221131156.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F05%2F20180522_gd_340_3%2Fgamersky_02origin_03_20185221131156.jpg&h=323d6835&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　雖然雙方簽約的具體費用沒有公佈，不過媒體揣測應該花費不低。"},{"pid":"8783301cbf33f96c0c42379893c0bcb4c9af75a5","tid":673651,"uid":46869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:57:13.000Z","msg":"拍av？"},{"pid":"e07d7d04ed6ce2ac54454d2fa6e68591a5f04353","tid":673651,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8783301cbf33f96c0c42379893c0bcb4c9af75a5","tid":673651,"uid":46869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:57:13.000Z","msg":"拍av？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:58:04.000Z","msg":"能鼓舞人、有創造性的聲音"},{"pid":"453d4328ff2dc2892e8532852a63f512670941be","tid":673651,"uid":134323,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:59:39.000Z","msg":"死黑鬼做總統時搞到一pat 屎咁仲好意思出黎拍戲"},{"p